、为什么家长不选择在孩子孩童阶段就把他们送到美国留学？</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><br></span></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7841,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492406646000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"为什么这些家长选择在中学阶段而不是小学阶段，也不是大学阶段把她送到美国留学呢？<div>因为小学阶段还不能自理，大学阶段的话，他，没有接受基础的美式教育，语言等方面没有一个环境培养。</div><div><br><div>为什么这些家长，在中学阶段把孩子送到美国，而不是欧洲，而不是澳大利亚，也不是新西兰呢？</div></div><div>因为美国这个国家代表着，最有创造力，最有经济活力的一个地方，在这个地方学习的话，显然天花板会更高。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7764,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492266148000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lizzie","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoBp020iboYUPZIm7Kn1xhUSodfrjYOqZaqpdScptV7c8cPTpxDbJ4b7k8icIOPu9qJ2OCVm5XwibfKk/0","content":"1.为什么这个趋势是上升的而不是下降的？<div>2.为什么是中学阶段而不是小学大学阶段?</div><div>3.为什么是美国而不是其他国家？</div><div>4.为什么是去上学而不是去工作生活?</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7653,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492078421000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"<p>1.关键词：中学阶段</p><p>为什么家长选择中学阶段把孩子送出去而不是大学？</p><p>－国内中学阶段课业重，面临的升学压力大。</p><p>－中学阶段人生观、价值观形成，应该去更发达的地方吸收更先进的理念和思维方式，如何创造性、批判性思维的养成。</p><p><br></p><p>2.关键词：美国</p><p>为什么不去其他国家而是美国？</p><p>－美国科技、经济最为发达，孩子可以接触到世界上最优秀的资源，提升自身的竞争力。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7560,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491952188000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoIfMsKLER8Nypic0GAEMQNhWH5ILCc3l1sO0iaB8nCIc9BLEdxIThXGnNtM55ozuBic03EicuCPictyib2/0","content":"反向提问1:为什么不在中学之前或者读完中学后送去美国读书？<div>回答：中学前孩子年龄太小，生活自理能力差，不容易适应国外生活；中学后，生活习惯已经养成，语言能力的提高也不及年龄小的时候，学业的压力和变化也更多多大。</div><div>反向提问2:为什么不送到其他国家？</div><div>回答：美国的教育质量比较受到公认，也有客观的评价体系，语言上英语相比欧洲其他语言更有基础。另外关于美国的留学产业更发达。</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7278,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491464399000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
